<p>Dr. Mansfield and his team have discovered a potential genomic signature to predict which patients with mesothelioma could benefit from immunotherapy.â€¯&amp;nbsp;<a href="https://newsnetwork.mayoclinic.org/discussion/mayo-clinic-researchers-discover-biomarker-for-predicting-immunotherapy-response-in-mesothelioma-cancer/">Read more</a>.</p>
